<li id="cite_note-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFMollerup2008">Mollerup, Asger (2008). <a href="http://www.sundial.thai-isan-lao.com/solstice-determination.html" class="external text" title="http://www.sundial.thai-isan-lao.com/solstice-determination.html" rel="nofollow">"Solstice Determination based on Observations"</a> (html)<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.sundial.thai-isan-lao.com/solstice-determination.html" class="external free" title="http://www.sundial.thai-isan-lao.com/solstice-determination.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.sundial.thai-isan-lao.com/solstice-determination.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2009-03-07</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Solstice+Determination+based+on+Observations&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Mollerup&amp;rft.aufirst=Asger&amp;rft.au=Mollerup%2C+Asger&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sundial.thai-isan-lao.com%2Fsolstice-determination.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Solstice"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
